From what I&#39;ve heard, it&#39;s not that the end of the world is coming, it&#39;s that a new age is coming; something is going to happen, a big change, but no one knows precisely what.  So it could be something similar to 911, where everyone sees things differently after that point, but not necessarily a big explosion like that; it could be a change in human collective consciousness.  This is the sort of thing the Mayan scholars are saying will happen. 

But I agree:  something is going to happen, even if it&#39;s subtle.

Jill




